---
---
<section class="newsletter" id="subscribe">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="newsletter-inner">
      <div class="newsletter-content">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">The Weekly Brief</div>
        <h2>Intelligence, not noise.</h2>
        <p>
          Every week: one distilled insight from the intersection of AI, hard money, 
          health, and freedom. Written for builders who want depth — not another 
          newsletter clogging their inbox with recycled takes.
        </p>
        <ul class="newsletter-bullets">
          <li>
            <span class="bullet-icon">→</span>
            Real-time documentation of a complete life rebuild
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="bullet-icon">→</span>
            Practical intelligence across all 6 Levers
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="bullet-icon">→</span>
            No ads, no sponsors, no fluff — ever
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="bullet-icon">→</span>
            Unsubscribe any time. No hard feelings.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="newsletter-form-wrap" id="newsletter">
        <div class="form-card">
          <div class="form-header">
            <div class="form-logo">RL</div>
            <div>
              <div class="form-title">The Weekly Brief</div>
              <div class="form-subtitle">Free. Always.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <iframe
            src="https://embeds.beehiiv.com/76c918da-6219-4e6b-8aee-e1e3a4f6c28f"
            data-test-id="beehiiv-embed"
            width="100%"
            height="320"
            frameborder="0"
            scrolling="no"
            style="border-radius: 4px; margin: 0; background: transparent;"
          ></iframe>
          <p class="form-disclaimer">
            Join builders who refuse to settle. No spam. One email per week.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .newsletter {
    background: var(--navy);
  }

  .newsletter-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .newsletter-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .newsletter-content p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--gray-light);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .newsletter-bullets {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .newsletter-bullets li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gray-light);
  }

  .bullet-icon {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.05rem;
  }

  .form-card {
    background: var(--navy-mid);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }

  .form-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .form-logo {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .form-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .form-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  .form-disclaimer {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .newsletter-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
